                        <h2 style="color:#002F86; font-size:22px;">Did You Know What’s New at Hamilton This Week?</h2>
                        <p><b>Ascend, Portal, and Jedi Updates</b><br/>
                        This week brings exciting improvements for our <b>Gift Officers, Alumni,</b> and the <b>BioDemo team</b> as part of the <b>October 27th release</b>.</p>
                        <p><b>Here’s What’s New When You Log In:</b></p>

                        <!-- Jedi Enhancements -->
                        <table width="100%">
                          <tr>
                            <td width="15%"><img src="https://image.contact.hamilton.edu/lib/fe3611737164057c721573/m/1/e0c08635-a515-4ac6-a7a5-6caae5e1c43c.png" width="80" /></td>
                            <td width="85%">
                              <b>Jedi Enhancements:</b> We’ve made Jedi even better! You can now search by <b>Class year, Student organizations, and Sport associations</b> — making it easier to find the right constituents. Gift Officers now have <b>a new default app and landing page</b>.
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>

                        <!-- Portal Improvements -->
                        <table width="100%">
                          <tr>
                            <td width="15%"><img src="https://image.contact.hamilton.edu/lib/fe3611737164057c721573/m/1/4669ec13-2d33-4298-886f-fc7e6444aba9.png" width="80" /></td>
                            <td width="85%">
                              <b>Portal Improvements:</b> The Portal has received a refresh for a cleaner and more accurate experience. Updates include improved display of <b>active records</b>, adjusted table labels, and <b>removal of unnecessary fields</b>.
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>

                        <!-- Presidential Briefings -->
                        <table width="100%">
                          <tr>
                            <td width="15%"><img src="https://image.contact.hamilton.edu/lib/fe3611737164057c721573/m/1/0b4ac644-564d-41e2-b40e-14b738c04aef.png" width="80" /></td>
                            <td width="85%">
                              <b>Presidential Briefings Relaunch:</b> The latest update removes the email-only step. In our next release, you’ll be able to <b>directly download and attach</b> briefings to an organization record.
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>

                        <!-- Society Flow -->
                        <table width="100%">
                          <tr>
                            <td width="15%"><img src="https://image.contact.hamilton.edu/lib/fe3611737164057c721573/m/1/2f33a2d2-56b7-40c5-9aa5-6e675babeb4e.png" width="80" /></td>
                            <td width="85%">
                              <b>Society Flow Updates:</b> Managing society records just got easier! Ascend now automatically keeps the <b>status flag in sync</b> with society records for smoother data consistency.
                            </td>
                          </tr>
